These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, rock, pop, salsa
1. the fan of rock is between the fan of pop and the fan of salsa##2
2. the fan of rock is on the left of the fan of pop##1
3. the fan of r&b is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |  3   |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | r&b | salsa | rock | pop |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, lemonade, fanta, soy-milk
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person drinking lemonade and the person drinking juice##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |  3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | lemonade | soy-milk | juice | fanta |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-3::.
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goldfish, frog, fish
1. the owner of the fish is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
2. the owner of the frog is between the owner of the goldfish and the owner of the fish##2
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2    |  3   |   4    |
| Pet   | chinchilla | fish | frog | goldfish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-4::.
There 4 different types of food: watermelon, blueberry, garlic, zucchini
1. the person eating garlic is between the person eating blueberry and the person eating watermelon##2
2. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
3. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| Food   | zucchini | blueberry | garlic | watermelon |

 #################################

 
